Three Times;;71;;85;;NC;;Three romantic tales take place in different eras. In "A Time for Love," set in 1966, a soldier (Chen Chang) meets an alluring pool-hall hostess (Shu Qi). "A Time for Freedom," set in 1911, focuses on a courtesan's relationship with a man during the Japanese occupation of Taiwan. In "A Time for Youth," set in 2005, a singer forsakes her female lover for a photographer.;;Romance,Lgbtq+;;Hsiao-hsien Hou;;2005;;Shu Qi,Chen Chang,Mei Fang,Liao Su-jen,Di Mei,Shi-Zheng Chen,Lee Pei-hsuan;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/three_times